The
brightest minds.

Navigating the world of digital marketing can often feel like being adrift in an ocean of technical jargon, dubious metrics and questionable tactics. That’s why we’ve worked hard to ensure we can be your compass. A Perth based, digital performance partner – not just another “digital marketing agency”. How? By using the best people and tools that evolve with the industry, rather than a pre-packaged solution. But mostly, we get there by listening. To you, your data, and your clients.

We're more than just another digital marketing agency. Discover the Bonfire difference.

Key Stats

  • 50+ of Australia's leading digital performance specialists in one local agency.

  • Trusted by Australia's leading brands, but proudly partnering many smaller ones with big aspirations.

  • Western Australia's leading independent Google Partner (accredited by Google).

  • Proud winners of numerous industry awards including Digital Agency of the Year 2021.

Performance Digital.

Data-driven digital marketing services that deliver "real" business growth. The kind that can be measured.

SEO

Looking for an SEO approach that is more than just a ranking quick fix?

Our award-winning organic search marketing methodology delivers an impressive and sustainable bottom line value. A carefully curated mix of human smarts, technical expertise and technology is the foundation of our remarkable track record.

Performance Media

Data-driven paid advertising strategies that connect with your customers at all stages of their buying journey.

As Perth’s leading independent Google Certified partner, we have a reputation for connecting the dots between search, social and display advertising. Our award-winning campaigns set the benchmark for well-constructed integrated campaigns, underpinned by data and ROI accountability.

Programmatic Advertising

Grow your brand with innovative advertising that leverages programmatic marketing, cutting-edge technology and a data-driven approach.

With a personalised approach to programmatic media, your marketing campaign won’t just reach more people; it’ll reach the right people.

Google Ads

As Perth’s leading independent Google Certified partner, our award-winning campaigns delight our clients with their impressive bottom line performance.

We’ve invested heavily in developing the perfect mix of industry-leading talent and innovative technologies to maximise the return on your advertising investment. We’ve mastered the science of helping you reach the right audience at the right time across Google to grow your business – profitably.

Social Media Advertising

Intelligent remarketing enables you to build “top of mind” recall and; strategic brand placement, for the exact moment when your customers are ready to act. Our digital marketing specialists are masters of interpreting behavioural data, consumer intent and creative messaging to build your brand.

When your advertising on Facebook, Instagram and LinkedIn must do more than just generate impressions. Our specialists have an enviable track record of creating paid social campaigns that deliver on real performance metrics – leads, sales and profit.

An agency of consultants that have the capability to develop strategies and execute them completely, with full accountability on performance and results.

49SELECT p.ID, pm.meta_value, p.post_type, p.post_status
FROM wp_posts AS p
INNER JOIN wp_postmeta AS pm
ON (pm.post_id = p.ID)
WHERE pm.meta_key = 'custom_permalink'
AND (pm.meta_value = ''
OR pm.meta_value = '/')
AND p.post_status != 'trash'
AND p.post_type != 'nav_menu_item'
ORDER BY FIELD(post_status,'publish','private','pending','draft','auto-draft','inherit'), FIELD(post_type,'post','page')
LIMIT 1

178SELECT wp_posts.*
FROM wp_posts
INNER JOIN wp_postmeta
ON ( wp_posts.ID = wp_postmeta.post_id )
WHERE 1=1
AND ( ( wp_postmeta.meta_key = 'featured'
AND wp_postmeta.meta_value = '1' ) )
AND wp_posts.post_type = 'solution'
AND ((wp_posts.post_status = 'publish'))
GROUP BY wp_posts.ID
ORDER BY wp_posts.menu_order, wp_posts.menu_order ASC
  1. WP_Query->get_posts()
    wp-includes/class-wp-query.php:3339
  2. WP_Query->query()
    wp-includes/class-wp-query.php:3824
  3. get_posts()
    wp-includes/post.php:2520

Configuration

The following PHP constants can be defined in your wp-config.php file in order to control the behaviour of Query Monitor:

QM_DB_EXPENSIVE
If an individual database query takes longer than this time to execute, it's considered "slow" and triggers a warning.
Default value: 0.05
QM_DISABLED
Disable Query Monitor entirely.
Default value: false
QM_DISABLE_ERROR_HANDLER
Disable the handling of PHP errors.
Default value: false
QM_ENABLE_CAPS_PANEL
Enable the Capability Checks panel.
Default value: false
QM_HIDE_CORE_ACTIONS
Hide WordPress core on the Hooks & Actions panel.
Default value: false
QM_HIDE_SELF
Hide Query Monitor itself from various panels. Set to false if you want to see how Query Monitor hooks into WordPress.
Default value: true
QM_NO_JQUERY
Don't specify jQuery as a dependency of Query Monitor. If jQuery isn't enqueued then Query Monitor will still operate, but with some reduced functionality.
Default value: false
QM_SHOW_ALL_HOOKS
In the Hooks & Actions panel, show every hook that has an action or filter attached (instead of every action hook that fired during the request).
Default value: false
QM_DB_SYMLINK
Allow the wp-content/db.php file symlink to be put into place during activation. Set to false to prevent the symlink creation.
Default value: true
